{"tid":2122289,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《暗夜星辰》令我流淚了 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T13:40:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9a2d7f5154bfea7f7842be809baf7569f5f418","tid":2122289,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200724/20962008/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200724%2F20962008%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6AjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=35f11507\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200724%2F20962008%2F&h=5a21cf3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200724/20962008/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《暗夜星辰》令我流淚了 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200724/large/1595493226_b1c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200724%2Flarge%2F1595493226_b1c2.jpg&h=67e11935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《暗夜星辰》截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n七月二十二日，香港警察與《鳳凰衛視》聯手製作的「反送中反警暴運動」紀錄片《暗夜星辰》終於上線了！我作為公正持平中立客觀的深深藍，觀賞過港台《鏗鏘集》的7&middot;21專輯後，當然也要瀏覽一下香港警方與中資媒體的合拍片，務求平衡立場，作出合理判斷。<br />\n<br />\n先撇開內容不談，這部紀錄片拍法異常拙劣單調，簡直悶出鳥來。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。喂佢哋真係唔識㗎喎。<br />\n<br />\n我可以代表藍絲們說：「我哋唔係要睇呢啲。」香港警察難得拍紀錄片，應該把握機遇，戳穿「外國勢力」如Illuminati等神秘組織的陰謀、追蹤反中亂港「顏色革命」的幕後黑手、解釋7&middot;21香港警察是否集體掉進蟲洞以致失蹤，或至少訪問一下為反送中義士提供免費性愛的「天使」&mdash;&mdash;這兒不妨同場訪問可敬的湯家驊大律師，叫他談談「衰十一」的嚴重法律後果。可是現在這齣《暗夜星辰》，以上內容一律欠奉，要故事無故事，要資訊無資訊，除了也許對失眠者有點用，我覺得簡直一無是處。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。，係笑到標眼淚。尾聲有位阿蛇笑着對鏡頭說：「正義會返返嚟我哋嗰度。」英文字幕是: &quot;Justice will be on our side.&quot;「會返返嚟」？Will be？言下之意，即正義現在沒有站在警察的一邊，站在你們那一邊的，是邪惡吧。這是全片最畫龍點睛的一句，大概也是唯一的真話，放到影片結尾更顯份量。認同的，請廣傳。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"99345dd78bf96b9e7836c66a01288034a959c89d","tid":2122289,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e9ad9770dd04a651e4697ab009e209a890742e","tid":2122289,"uid":104106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"我要認我跳住咁睇咗, 想睇下會唔會玩陰謀論, 外國勢力,驚唔驚制裁之類<br />\n<br />\n結論係好撚悶, 我睇藍絲比人打嘅片段仲多, 我仲高興<br />\n成班就係圍爐,扮慘<br />\n依家成班仲要出曬樣, 都唔知係咪特登. <br />\n外國情報機關洗少啲力水做記錄"},{"pid":"239d708dba6469f3d90b8a4168ef4db9668663af","tid":2122289,"uid":13308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"一個有公權力既警隊成日sell煽情弱勢<br />\n同女人一喊二鬧三上吊有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72f86768c8a32a8e8da4f301bd12b607851cb89","tid":2122289,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:38:43.000Z","msg":"我都流淚呀 估唔到黑警可以無恥到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a668033a217011b9488c9e454ddfa87f33f2bde7","tid":2122289,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"係咪李力持拍嘅啫"},{"pid":"afa4528470cd6f045dfb0896625065bf9dceb966","tid":2122289,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f863767aec932ef4daa5a36031100d7fe74bed1","tid":2122289,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"Justice will be on our side.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad88efa2973c95bb7d0c211d1303293f3ed7c51f","tid":2122289,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f863767aec932ef4daa5a36031100d7fe74bed1","tid":2122289,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"Justice will be on our side.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"Prevail 太深？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}